  "text": "Traditionally, Multi Criteria Decision Making (MCDM) methods have been widely used in partner selection, [CITATION_1] . In this study a hybrid version of one such technique is used to evaluate the relevant partner selection factors, the DEMATEL (Decision-making trial and evaluation laboratory) method. The DEMATEL model has been successfully applied in many fields and areas, such as outsourcing, project management and marketing including the use of Fuzzy DEMATEL in partner selection and evaluation studies [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
